The principle of sustainable development permeates NDP5. As such, the plan frames the achievement of progress within a framework of ensuring the ability of future generations to thrive. In the same spirit, NDP5 has four key goals, namely;
* Achieve Inclusive, Sustainable and Equitable Economic Growth,
* Build Capable and Healthy Human Resources;
* Ensure Sustainable Environment and Enhance Resilience; and
* Promote Good Governance through Effective Institutions
